pullRequest.body:
We define strong natural transformations of oplax functors, and provide API for going between strong and oplax natural transformations. We also move & rename the file `NaturalTransformation.lean`, which defines oplax natural transformations, to `NaturalTransformation/Oplax.lean`. This should make it easier to also add lax natural transformations in the future.

```suggestion
structure StrongOplaxNatTrans (F G : OplaxFunctor B C) where
```
The name has to be changed, otherwise there will be a problem with lax/pseudo-functors.

As you are generating `simps` lemmas, it may be appropriate to give an explicit name to this instance (and put it in the `Pseudofunctor` namespace), so that it will look better when we need to invoke these lemmas explicitly.
